      "text": [
        ": مَنْ قَرَأَ وَ أَکْثَرَ مِنْ قِرَاءَهِ الْقَارِعَهِ آمَنَهُ اللَّهُ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ مِنْ فِتْنَهِ الدَّجَّالِ أَنْ یُؤْمِنَ بِهِ وَ مِنْ فَیْحِ جَهَنَّمَ إِنْ شَاءَ اللَّهُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1. From the previous chain from al-Hussain from Ismail b. al-Zubayr from ’Amru b. Thabit from Abi Ja’far (a.s.) who said: “Whoever recites this Surah would be kept safe by Allah from acting upon the mischief of Dajjal and he would remain safe from the chastisement of Hell.”"
        ]
